metadata.name: Rekt-flections
metadata.description:
'Rektflections' is a genesis foundation piece and original work from the limited collection titled: Portmanteau by DNS_ERR.

'Rektflections' showcases the deep state of reflection crypto native extractoors are currently in by Integrating Ben Zank's 'Deep State of Reflection' & OSF's 'Rekt-Guy'.

https://superrare.com/benzank
https://superrare.com/OSF

Put simply, 'Rektflections' evokes the feeling of a flippoors portfolio being down 90% during crypto winter.
 
"Diamond hands"

Thank You,
DNS_ERR
